Basic raytracer using the MinilibX.

USAGE :
./miniRT <scene>.rt [-save|--save]
	Render the <scene>.rt file using the MinilibX. Press space to switch camera.
-save, --save
	Render the <scene>.rt file in a save.bmp file (only the first camera).

EXAMPLE :
./miniRT scenes/columns.rt -save
